Description: Provides tools for importing, parsing, and analysing raw actigraphy
    data. Supports common device file formats, computes standard rest-activity
    variables (interdaily stability, intradaily variability, relative amplitude,
    L5, M10), and assembles tidy data frames ready for downstream chronobiological
    analysis. Designed to complement slumbR in the Circadia Lab ecosystem.
